[{"location":"library/all_index/","page":"Index","title":"Index","text":"CurrentModule = Learn","category":"page"},{"location":"library/all_index/#Learn.jl","page":"Index","title":"Learn.jl","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"library/all_index/","page":"Index","title":"Index","text":"","category":"page"},{"location":"library/all_index/","page":"Index","title":"Index","text":"Modules = [Learn]","category":"page"},{"location":"library/all_index/#Learn.add-Tuple{Any,Any}","page":"Index","title":"Learn.add","text":"add(x, y)\n\nReturns x + y\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"library/all_index/#Learn.add-Tuple{Int64,Int64}","page":"Index","title":"Learn.add","text":"add(x::Int64, y::Int64) -> Int64\n\nReturns x + y\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"library/all_index/#Learn.add-Union{Tuple{T}, Tuple{T,T}} where T<:Number","page":"Index","title":"Learn.add","text":"add(x::T, y::T) -> T\n\nReturns x + y\n\nExamples\n\njulia> add(1+3im,3+5im)\n4 + 8im\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"create_package/#Create-new-package","page":"Create Package","title":"Create new package","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"create_package/","page":"Create Package","title":"Create Package","text":"First add PkgTemplates","category":"page"},{"location":"create_package/","page":"Create Package","title":"Create Package","text":"(@v1.5) pkg> add PkgTemplates","category":"page"},{"location":"create_package/","page":"Create Package","title":"Create Package","text":"Then use the following template","category":"page"},{"location":"create_package/","page":"Create Package","title":"Create Package","text":"using PkgTemplates\nt = Template(; \n    user=\"binnisb\",\n    julia=v\"1.5\",\n    plugins=[\n        Git(; manifest=true, ssh=true, jl=true),\n        Tests(;project=true),\n        GitHubActions(; x86=false),\n        Codecov(),\n        Documenter{GitHubActions}(),\n        Develop(),\n        Citation(;readme=true)\n    ],\n)\nt(\"Learn\")","category":"page"},{"location":"create_package/","page":"Create Package","title":"Create Package","text":"Create the GitHub reopository Learn.jl and push master to it.","category":"page"},{"location":"create_package/","page":"Create Package","title":"Create Package","text":"To be able to push the docs to GitHub pages, I needed to follow DocumenterTools.genkeys and create the deploy key and DOCUMENTER_KEY secret.","category":"page"},{"location":"create_package/","page":"Create Package","title":"Create Package","text":"To run DocTests within src/*.jl files you need to add a line to [docs/make.jl]:","category":"page"},{"location":"create_package/","page":"Create Package","title":"Create Package","text":"DocMeta.setdocmeta!(Learn, :DocTestSetup, :(using Learn); recursive=true)","category":"page"},{"location":"create_package/","page":"Create Package","title":"Create Package","text":"which makes the Learn module available in all Docstrings in the julia files. If you create submodules, that might need some extra manipulations to get that working.","category":"page"},{"location":"create_package/","page":"Create Package","title":"Create Package","text":"I also chaged the .github/workflows/ci.yml to call a file make_doctest.jl for running the tests, and then calling make.jl to build the docs and deploy. I refactored out the library calls and setup needed for both.","category":"page"},{"location":"create_package/","page":"Create Package","title":"Create Package","text":"Then from terminal:","category":"page"},{"location":"create_package/","page":"Create Package","title":"Create Package","text":"# From the Learn.jl folder\njulia --project=docs  docs/make_doctest.jl  # Runs the Doctests\njulia --project=docs  docs/make.jl  # Builds documents and runs the Doctests\njulia --project=.  test/runtests.jl  # Runs the test suite for Learn","category":"page"},{"location":"#Learn.jl","page":"Home","title":"Learn.jl","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"This package is intendet to gather my learnings and explorations using Julia.","category":"page"}]
